query:
SELECT
            TO_CHAR(taken_at_local, 'YYYY-MM') as "month_id!",
            COUNT(*)::INT AS "count!",
            array_agg(width::real / height::real) AS "ratios!"
        FROM
            media_item
        WHERE
            user_id = $1 AND deleted = false
        GROUP BY
            TO_CHAR(taken_at_local, 'YYYY-MM')
        ORDER BY
            "month_id!" DESC
